6'),(5730,269,'essb_cached_image','https://maskell.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/thumbnail-video.jpg'),(5787,145,'flexible_content_modules_0_margin_amount','95'),(5788,145,'_flexible_content_modules_0_margin_amount','field_5af440354f167'),(5789,145,'flexible_content_modules_1_left_heading','Lean Accounting: Financial Management for the Lean Organization'),(5790,145,'_flexible_content_modules_1_left_heading','field_5af464d43c613'),(5791,145,'flexible_content_modules_1_left_content','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To achieve success, a lean organization must develop an effective and efficient management accounting function that complements its financial accounting system to provide a knowledge base for effectively making decisions about the future (this is critical because the focus of financial accounting is on past activity). A lean management accounting system makes relevant information available to decision makers on a timely basis.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a broader context, lean accounting is a financial learning system for the entire organization, not just the accounting function. Because the economics of lean changes the relationships between operations and financial numbers, the whole business must learn the new relationships and incorporate the dynamic context of these relationships in all financial analysis. </span></p>\r\n&nbsp;'),(5792,145,'_flexible_content_modules_1_left_content','field_5af464f43c615'),(5793,145,'flexible_content_modules_1_youtube_id','nZAET69xwb4'),(5794,145,'_flexible_content_modules_1_youtube_id','field_5af465053c616'),(5795,145,'flexible_content_modules_1_space_after','space-after-medium'),(5796,145,'_flexible_content_modules_1_space_after','field_5af465d9ade7c'),(5803,145,'flexible_content_modules_3_quote','BMA Inc. has been a tremendous help to us. Their experience and knowledge of lean is outstanding, and essential to the success with Lean Accounting. BMA does an excellent job in continuously linking these two together. Lean Accounting does not make sense without lean and vice versa.In facing the complexity of a global business, with numerous plants and divisions, BMA’s insight into systems and IT issues has also been crucial. Discussions tend to accelerate in the wrong direction, especially when it comes to this critical area. These unfruitful discussions disappear as BMA Inc. guides the improvement processes with great professionalism.'),(5804,145,'_flexible_content_modules_3_quote','field_5af449d40a398'),(5805,145,'flexible_content_modules_3_quote_author','Division Finance Manager, International Manufacturing Company'),(5806,145,'_flexible_content_modules_3_quote_author','field_5af449ec0a399'),(5807,145,'flexible_content_modules_3_background_color','#db624a'),(5808,145,'_flexible_content_modules_3_background_color','field_5af449f70a39a'),(5809,145,'flexible_content_modules_3_space_after','space-after-medium'),(5810,145,'_flexible_content_modules_3_space_after','field_5af44a180a39b'),(5827,117,'buy_books','https://www.amazon.com/default/e/B000APPV4U/ref=sr_ntt_srch_lnk_1?qid=1530024930&sr=8-1&redirectedFromKindleDbs=true'),(5828,117,'_buy_books','field_5b509bcc7a3bf'),(5889,146,'flexible_content_modules_3_text','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Lean Accounting Pilot Kaizen Events</strong></h2>'),(5890,146,'_flexible_content_modules_3_text','field_5af4423560e78'),(5891,146,'flexible_content_modules_3_space_after','space-after-none'),(5892,146,'_flexible_content_modules_3_space_after','field_5af4425f60e79'),(5893,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_0_icon',''),(5894,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_0_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5895,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_0_heading','Event 1: Lean Accounting Assessment'),(5896,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_0_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5897,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_0_content','On Day 1, BMA will visit and conduct a detailed assessment of the current state of your Lean transformation plan, management accounting system, and financial management practices. On Days 2 &amp; 3, BMA will present our standard two-day Practicing Lean Accounting class, which will include the results of our assessment.'),(5898,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_0_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5899,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_1_icon',''),(5900,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_1_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5901,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_1_heading','Event 2: Value Stream Identification & Organization (optional)'),(5902,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_1_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5903,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_1_content','If your company is early in its Lean journey, you may not yet have identified your value streams. If this is the case, we recommend a 3-day kaizen event to complete this essential task for a Lean Accounting transformation plan. In this kaizen, your company will define the operational flows within the company, determine the value stream teams required to support the lean enterprise, and determine the most appropriate organizational structure.'),(5904,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_1_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5905,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_2_icon',''),(5906,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_2_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5907,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_2_heading','Event 3: Lean Performance Measurements'),(5908,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_2_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5909,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_2_content','Using the BMA Linkage Chart process, this kaizen event will develop and implement integrated metrics for daily cell measures, weekly value stream measures, and monthly strategic Lean measures.'),(5910,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_2_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5911,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_3_icon',''),(5912,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_3_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5913,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_3_heading','Event 4: Value Stream Income Statement & Capacity'),(5914,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_3_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5915,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_3_content','In this kaizen event, a value stream income statement will be created for the pilot value stream(s). Value stream capacity will also be calculated using the BMA capacity calculation template.'),(5916,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_3_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5917,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_4_icon',''),(5918,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_4_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5919,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_4_heading','Event 5: Financial Management Practices using the Box Score'),(5920,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_4_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5921,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_4_content','This kaizen event will develop new standard work practices for financial analysis using the Box Score. The implementation team will perform Box Score analysis of actual company business cases related to investment analysis, make/buy decisions, profitability analysis, and measuring the financial impact of continuous improvement to develop new standard work practices.'),(5922,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block_4_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5923,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_column_block','5'),(5924,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_column_block','field_5af4644a313dc'),(5925,146,'flexible_content_modules_4_space_after','space-after-small'),(5926,146,'_flexible_content_modules_4_space_after','field_5af464de3c614'),(5953,146,'flexible_content_modules_5_text','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Advanced Lean Accounting Kaizen Events</h2>'),(5954,146,'_flexible_content_modules_5_text','field_5af4423560e78'),(5955,146,'flexible_content_modules_5_space_after','space-after-none'),(5956,146,'_flexible_content_modules_5_space_after','field_5af4425f60e79'),(5957,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_0_icon',''),(5958,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_0_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5959,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_0_heading','Event 6: ERP Simplification & Transaction Elimination'),(5960,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_0_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5961,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_0_content','This kaizen event identifies the wasteful transactions in your business operations and systems. The implementation team will develop a maturity path for transforming your current accounting controls into Lean accounting controls. Transaction processing related to production control, purchasing, inventory tracking, work orders, and payables will be improved.'),(5962,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_0_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5963,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_1_icon',''),(5964,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_1_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(5965,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_1_heading','Event 7: Lean Inventory Valuation'),(5966,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_1_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(5967,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_1_content','In this kaizen event the implementation team will develop simplified inventory valuation methodologies to replace standard costing-based inventory valuation.'),(5968,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block_1_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(5969,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_column_block','2'),(5970,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_column_block','field_5af4644a313dc'),(5971,146,'flexible_content_modules_6_space_after','space-after-none'),(5972,146,'_flexible_content_modules_6_space_after','field_5af464de3c614'),(5973,146,'flexible_content_modules_7_background_image','97'),(5974,146,'_flexible_content_modules_7_background_image','field_5afaefab6b23b'),(5975,146,'flexible_content_modules_7_primary_heading','Download Sample Agenda for Pilot Event'),(5976,146,'_flexible_content_modules_7_primary_heading','field_5afaefc46b23c'),(5977,146,'flexible_content_modules_7_secondary_heading',''),(5978,146,'_flexible_content_modules_7_secondary_heading','field_5afaefd56b23d'),(5979,146,'flexible_content_modules_7_button_label','Download Now'),(5980,146,'_flexible_content_modules_7_button_label','field_5afaefe56b23e'),(5981,146,'flexible_content_modules_7_button_link','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:67:\"/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Lean-Accounting-Pilot-Detailed-Plan.xls\";s:6:\"target\";s:6:\"_blank\";}'),(5982,146,'_flexible_content_modules_7_button_link','field_5afaeff56b23f'),(5983,146,'flexible_content_modules_7_space_after','space-after-medium'),(5984,146,'_flexible_content_modules_7_space_after','field_5afb3272e482f'),(5985,146,'flexible_content_modules_8_youtube_id','C0_q2d0Xx0Q'),(5986,146,'_flexible_content_modules_8_youtube_id','field_5af604f10e686'),(5987,146,'flexible_content_modules_8_space_after','space-after-medium'),(5988,146,'_flexible_content_modules_8_space_after','field_5af604fc0e687'),(5989,146,'flexible_content_modules_9_text','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lean for Accounting and Office Functions</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith over 30 years of experience implementing Lean practices in accounting functions and other office processes, BMA can provide consulting services to facilitate your company’s accounting and/or office function Lean transformation.\r\n\r\nThe goal of our Lean transformation consulting services for accounting and office functions is to train and develop your implementation team to provide them with the skills, experience and tools necessary to continue a Lean transformation.\r\n\r\nOur consulting services are customized to meet your specific needs. Here are some of examples of consulting services we can provide for accounting and office functions.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Develop lean performance measurements</li>\r\n 	<li>Design &amp; implement visual management practices to manage, control and improve a process</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop standard work for process team to maintain and use visual management boards</li>\r\n 	<li>Value stream mapping</li>\r\n 	<li>Value stream management practices</li>\r\n 	<li>Continuous improvement practices &amp; kaizen</li>\r\n 	<li>Design pull system &amp; implement single piece flow</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAccounting - specific consulting services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Reduce month-end close process time</li>\r\n 	<li>Reduce annual budgeting process time</li>\r\n 	<li>Eliminate waste and create flow in accounting transaction processing, such as payables and receivables</li>\r\n</ul>'),(5990,146,'_flexible_content_modules_9_text','field_5af4423560e78'),(5991,146,'flexible_content_modules_9_space_after','space-after-small'),(5992,146,'_flexible_content_modules_9_space_after','field_5af4425f60e79'),(5993,146,'flexible_content_modules_10_text','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lean Management</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;'),(5994,146,'_flexible_content_modules_10_text','field_5af4423560e78'),(5995,146,'flexible_content_modules_10_space_after','space-after-none'),(5996,146,'_flexible_content_modules_10_space_after','field_5af4425f60e79'),(6003,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_0_icon',''),(6004,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_0_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6005,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_0_heading','Value Stream Identification & Organization'),(6006,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_0_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6007,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_0_content','In this 3-day kaizen event, your company will define the operational flows within the company, determine the value stream teams required to support the Lean enterprise, determine the most appropriate organizational structure, and develop a practical action plan for introducing these value streams. This kaizen event is relevant to any organization in any industry, and to any function within an organization.'),(6008,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_0_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(6009,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_1_icon',''),(6010,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_1_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6011,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_1_heading','Value Stream Management'),(6012,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_1_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6013,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_1_content','This 3-day kaizen event is designed to show new value stream managers how to manage, control, and improve their value streams. The event demonstrates how Lean practices and Lean Accounting fit together into a cohesive value stream management system for sustained growth, increased value, waste elimination, and financial success.'),(6014,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_1_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(6015,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_2_icon',''),(6016,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_2_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6017,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_2_heading','Value Stream Mapping'),(6018,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_2_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6019,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_2_content','This kaizen event (3-5 days) is designed to teach a team the entire value stream mapping process. In this event, a team will draw a current state value stream map for a specific value stream, learn the standard steps required to build Lean flow into the value stream, design &amp; map the future state, and develop a practical action plan to make the future state a reality.'),(6020,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_2_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(6021,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_3_icon',''),(6022,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_3_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6023,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_3_heading','Lean Strategy Development for Executive Teams'),(6024,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_3_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6025,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_3_content','In this 3-day kaizen event, the executive team will develop a plan to implement a comprehensive Lean strategy, which will include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Defining the strategic goals of your company’s Lean transformation</li>\r\n 	<li>Establishing long-term strategic steps for your Lean transformation</li>\r\n 	<li>Defining the operational and financial goals of your Lean transformation</li>\r\n 	<li>Developing the fundamental principles of Lean thinking</li>\r\n 	<li>Developing a Lean culture</li>\r\n 	<li>Defining the role of executive leaders</li>\r\n</ul>'),(6026,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_3_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(6027,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_4_icon',''),(6028,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_4_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6029,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_4_heading','Lean Product Development and Project Management'),(6030,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_4_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6031,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_4_content','This kaizen event (3-5 days) is designed to pilot the Lean transformation process for product development or project management. In this event, the current state will be mapped to identify where waste is occurring. The team will then work to identify how standard Lean practices can be used to make the processes much faster, creating more value, and flawlessly launching the product or product in designing a future state. Flow and pull processes will be created, as well as an improvement plan to achieve the future state. The team will develop a visual management board to measure and manage flow.'),(6032,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_4_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(6033,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_5_icon',''),(6034,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_5_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6035,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_5_heading','Lean Sales, Operations and Financial Planning'),(6036,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_5_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6037,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_5_content','Lean organizations are very well planned and have effective sales, operations, and financial planning processes. This 3-5 day kaizen event is designed to bring together the elements of continuous improvement, Lean accounting box scores, and forecasting into a Lean sales, operations and financial planning process which will provide improved demand and capacity forecasting, optimize flow and continuous improvement, and create valid, actionable rolling forecasts.'),(6038,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_5_content','field_5af4646d313df'),(6039,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_6_icon',''),(6040,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_6_icon','field_5af46458313dd'),(6041,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_6_heading','Lean Strategy Deployment'),(6042,146,'_flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_6_heading','field_5af46465313de'),(6043,146,'flexible_content_modules_11_column_block_6_content','Lean strategy deployment (also known as Hoshin) starts with the executive team setting the company’s strategy and goals, which is then deployed through each value stream and administrative function across the Lean organization. This 3-day kaizen event is designed to develop actual policy deployment processes for your company, which includes “X-charts”, value streams, cells, and de